6 Stages
1 Jail

Jail & Spawn Klickz
Stage 1-3 Klickz
Stage 4&5 Shoop
Stage 6 ChiChin

Klickz started this map quite a while ago but he went inactive, so i had to finish the map.
I didn't have any map experience and was struggling with some problems.
But finally I got it.
It's my first map so I would be glad about some reasonable feedback.

Special thanks to Chuck Norris for letting me use his server for a beta test
Also i want to thank all the beta testers.
